---
title: Creamy Cajun Spiced Chorizo Orzo with Peas and Toasted Breadcrumb Topping
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Creamy Cajun Spiced Chorizo Orzo in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
